{
  "title": "Salty Shaggy Lazy-Sunday French Serrano Ham Pilaf",
  "description": "A fresh and shaggy french brigtany dish featuring a slow-cooked pilaf of rice with salty serrano ham. Perfect for lazy Sundays.",
  "cuisine": "French (Brittany)",
